result.execSummary:
The defendant Jerry D Hubbart was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case.

  • 4th Degree Sexual Assault [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.225(3m).
  • Strangulation and Suffocation [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.235(1).
  • False Imprisonment [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.30.
  • Intimidate Victim/Use or Attempt Force [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class G felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.45(1).
  • Substantial Battery-Intend Bodily Harm [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class I felony, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(2).
